values: Hi! My journal is friends only...leave me a comment that tells me who you are and why you want to be my friend to be added. I'll most likely add you, but I want to know WHY you actually want to read this thing. If you're unfamiliar with Livejournal, friends only means that you have to have a Livejournal account and be listed as one of my friends in order to read the entries. It's free, so if you're really dying to read about my lack of a life, sign up.
